# Releases Folder

This folder contains release/version-specific design documentation.

Use when design work is organized by release version rather than feature.

Example structure:
```
releases/
├── v1.0/
│   ├── README.md
│   ├── navigation.md
│   └── features/
│       └── ...
├── v1.1/
│   └── ...
└── v2.0/
    └── ...
```

Each release folder can contain:
- README.md with release overview
- Feature-specific documentation
- Release notes drafts
- Migration guides
